<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <%- include('partials/head', { title: '负载均衡测试站点' }) %>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('partials/nav', { active: 'home', serverIP: serverIP }) %>

    <div class="container">
        <!-- ============================== HERO ============================== -->
        <section class="hero">
            <div class="hero__left">
                <h1 class="hero__title">负载均衡测试站点</h1>
                <p class="hero__subtitle">会话保持 · 长连接 · F5 故障注入 · 多 Pod 路由验证</p>
                <div class="hero__meta">
                    <div class="hero__meta-item">
                        <span class="hero__meta-label">当前 Pod</span>
                        <span class="hero__meta-value"><%= serverIP %></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="hero__meta-item">
                        <span class="hero__meta-label">客户端 IP</span>
                        <span class="hero__meta-value"><%= clientIP %></span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="hero__meta-item">
                        <span class="hero__meta-label">本机时间</span>
                        <span class="hero__meta-value live-clock"><%= currentTime %></span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="hero__right">
                <div class="hero__status hero__status--<%= faultMode === 'none' ? 'ok' : 'down' %>">
                    <div class="hero__status-icon">
                        <% if (faultMode === 'none') { %>
                            <%- include('partials/icon', { name: 'heart-pulse', size: 22 }) %>
                        <% } else { %>
                            <%- include('partials/icon', { name: 'alert-triangle', size: 22 }) %>
                        <% } %>
                    </div>
                    <div class="hero__status-body">
                        <div class="hero__status-label">F5 Monitor</div>
                        <div class="hero__status-value">
                            <% if (faultMode === 'none') { %>健康 (200)<% } else { %>故障: <%= faultMode %><% } %>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <button class="btn btn-sm btn-secondary" onclick="location.reload()">
                    <%- include('partials/icon', { name: 'refresh-cw', size: 13 }) %>
                    刷新
                </button>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- ============================== LOGIN BANNER ============================== -->
        <% if (isLoggedIn) { %>
            <div class="status status--success hero__login-banner">
                <%- include('partials/icon', { name: 'check', size: 14 }) %>
                已登录用户 <strong><%= username %></strong>，会话ID: <code><%= sessionId %></code>
            </div>
        <% } %>

        <!-- ============================== 4 功能卡片 ============================== -->
        <h2 class="section-title">
            <%- include('partials/icon', { name: 'list', size: 18 }) %>
            测试入口
        </h2>
        <div class="feature-grid">
            <a href="/login" class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-card__icon feature-card__icon--blue">
                    <%- include('partials/icon', { name: 'log-in', size: 20 }) %>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card__title">登录测试</div>
                <div class="feature-card__desc">创建会话，验证负载均衡器对 JSESSIONID 的保持行为</div>
            </a>
            <a href="/session-test" class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-card__icon feature-card__icon--green">
                    <%- include('partials/icon', { name: 'shield', size: 20 }) %>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card__title">会话验证</div>
                <div class="feature-card__desc">检查会话 ID、Cookie、X-Forwarded-For 头部，验证服务器路由一致性</div>
            </a>
            <a href="/long-connection" class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-card__icon feature-card__icon--cyan">
                    <%- include('partials/icon', { name: 'plug', size: 20 }) %>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card__title">长连接业务</div>
                <div class="feature-card__desc">WebSocket / SSE / 长轮询，验证 F5 长连接透传与超时配置</div>
            </a>
            <a href="/admin/fault" class="feature-card">
                <div class="feature-card__icon feature-card__icon--orange">
                    <%- include('partials/icon', { name: 'settings', size: 20 }) %>
                </div>
                <div class="feature-card__title">故障注入</div>
                <div class="feature-card__desc">修改 <code>/health</code> 响应，触发 F5 action on service down</div>
            </a>
        </div>

        <!-- ============================== 实时数据 ============================== -->
        <h2 class="section-title">
            <span class="live-dot"></span>
            实时连接数据
            <span class="section-title__sub">本 Pod 当前活跃连接 (SSE 推送)</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="stats-grid stats-grid--lg">
            <div class="stat-box stat-box--ws">
                <div class="stat-num" id="stat-ws"><%= connStats.websocket %></div>
                <div class="stat-label">WebSocket</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-box stat-box--sse">
                <div class="stat-num" id="stat-sse"><%= connStats.sse %></div>
                <div class="stat-label">SSE</div>
            </div>
            <div class="stat-box stat-box--lp">
                <div class="stat-num" id="stat-lp"><%= connStats.longPoll %></div>
                <div class="stat-label">长轮询</div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- ============================== 使用说明 ============================== -->
        <div class="help-block">
            <strong>使用说明</strong>
            <ul>
                <li>此站点用于测试负载均衡器的会话保持功能</li>
                <li>点击"登录测试"进入登录页面，登录后可查看会话是否在多次请求中保持一致</li>
                <li>刷新页面可查看请求是否路由到同一服务器</li>
                <li><strong>长连接业务</strong>：测试 WebSocket / SSE / 长轮询在 F5 上的表现</li>
                <li><strong>故障注入</strong>：修改本 Pod 的 <code>/health</code> 响应，让 F5 HTTP monitor 探测到业务故障</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script src="/js/clock.js"></script>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    <script>
    // 订阅 /api/fault/stream 拿 conn_stats 实时更新
    try {
        const es = new EventSource('/api/fault/stream');
        es.onmessage = (ev) => {
            try {
                const msg = JSON.parse(ev.data);
                if (msg.type === 'conn_stats' && msg.stats) {
                    document.getElementById('stat-ws').textContent  = msg.stats.websocket || 0;
                    document.getElementById('stat-sse').textContent = msg.stats.sse || 0;
                    document.getElementById('stat-lp').textContent  = msg.stats.longPoll || 0;
                }
            } catch (e) { /* ignore */ }
        };
        es.onerror = () => { /* EventSource auto-reconnect */ };
    } catch (e) { /* EventSource not supported */ }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
